      "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThe documentation on dynamic forms is confusing and leaves many questions unanswered:\r\n\r\n* Why is there a `main.ts` all of a sudden?\r\n* Why is there a second bootstrap call necessary (`platformBrowserDynamic().bootstrapModule(AppModule);`)?\r\n   I.e., why doesn't `@angular/platform-browser-dynamic` automatically add a hook to `@NgModule({bootstrap: [AppComponent]})` in `app.module.ts` so it would run automatically?\r\n* What is the general guideline to follow with dynamic forms when there are animations supposed to run when adding or deleting items (e.g. fade-out)?\r\n\r\n### What is the affected URL?\r\n\r\nhttps://angular.io/guide/dynamic-form\r\n\r\n### Please provide a screenshot if possible\r\n\r\n![screenshot](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/9283914/145907149-37a50321-c79f-416c-8461-faccd50b4cf8.png)\r\n",
